30 appropriate comanagement or transfer of high-risk patients to other
31 healthcare professionals as needed; and
32 (5) Prescribe and administer drugs listed in Schedules III — V
33 without a collaborative practice agreement or supervision of another
34 healthcare professional when performing healthcare services;
